    g - Create
    m - module
    c - component
    s - Serviace

Create a core module

PS C:\Demo\client\src\app> ng g m core
Creating a Module


Creating a Module in New Folder
PS C:\Demo\client\src\app> ng g m shop

Creating a component without folder (flat)
PS C:\Demo\client\src\app\shop> ng g c shop --flat --skip--test 
    
Creating Serviace inside the Shop folder
PS C:\Demo\client\src\app\shop> ng g s shop --skip-tests --flat

Creating a component in new folder in the Shop folder

PS C:\Demo\client\src\app\shop> ng g c product-item --skip-tests